room_title: Escape room "Defcon 1" by 1 Hour to Escape in Dallas-Fort Worth
room_description: In the midst of the Cold War, you and your team get hired as janitors at a high-clearance US military facility. (With all that heightened security comes lots of extra cleaning up!) On your first day, your team accidentally triggers the launch sequence for a nuclear bomb, and with all the regular personnel gone overnight, itâ€™s up to you to stop the bomb before launch in exactly one hour.
